COMMENT ON COLUMN loops.mock_data_note IS 'What the seed data is designed to show.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN loops.next_suggestion IS 'Suggestion for the next loop.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN loops.commit_hash IS 'Git SHA where this loop first landed.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN loops.commit_date IS 'ISO date of the commit.';

