COMMENT ON TABLE systems IS 'Table: Systems — named physical configurations of charges. Groups Charges into testable scenarios (hydrogen atom, NaCl pair, triangle of charges, etc.).';
COMMENT ON COLUMN systems.system_id IS 'Unique identifier';
